  tglClearShot.Value,
  Blank(),
  If(!IsBlank(AddPic_Screenshot.Media), AddPic_Screenshot.Media, Parent.Default)
)


After submit (see Â§6), reset the toggle:

Reset(tglClearShot); Reset(AddPic_Screenshot)


B) Button approach

Insert a Button â€œClearâ€.

OnSelect:

