Quick Troubleshooting

No thumbnail in list: Ensure you updated the Image column (screenshot) â€” not just Attachments or a Hyperlink column. Confirm the view displays screenshot.

Image didnâ€™t save: Verify screenshot_DataCard.Update exactly as above, and that AddPic_Screenshot sits inside the card.

Editing existing item shows old image: Thatâ€™s correct if you didnâ€™t pick a new one. Use the Remove flow (toggle/button) to clear, then submit.

Multiple screenshots: The Image column stores one picture. Keep Attachments for additional images; or add screenshot_2 (another Image column) if you want a second primary image.
